about.summary: An implementation of time.monotonic() for Python 2 & Python 3.

name: monotonic
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "monotonic" %}
{% set version = "1.2" %}
{% set md5 = "d14c93aabc3d6af25ef086b032b123cf" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: {{ md5 }}

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - monotonic

about:
  home: https://github.com/atdt/monotonic
  license: Apache License Version 2.0
  summary: An implementation of time.monotonic() for Python 2 & Python 3.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - alimanfoo
    - anguslees
